{"tid":1914813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【護旗手政協藍店搏見報】何超蓮賣平麵送口罩俾老人家","createTime":"2020-03-07T19:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T17:29:40.000Z","uid":175314,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5a969c151234b57c31b637d8cafd69b4a4325f","tid":1914813,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T19:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFJ1gEp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFJ1gEp.jpg&h=2ee2ac80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>新聞內容轉發自香港蘋果日報</ins><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐香港，全港市民爭撲防疫物資，亦有一些慈善團體就搜羅口罩，派給長者及低收入人士，好似賭王三房千金何超蓮透過她與友人創辦的Smile with us HK多次向長者、清潔工、露宿者以及低收入人士派發口罩及消毒噴霧，實行出錢出力。<br />\n<br />\n超蓮今日在其IG再發帖文，表示在銅鑼灣及旺角開的台灣牛肉麵店，推出多個優惠給市民抗疫，當中主力想幫長者，例如會送口罩給長者食客，當中65歲以上的長者幫襯會有六折優惠，成本價資助長者，為他們打氣。超蓮回覆《蘋果》時表示：「睇到新聞知道好多長者重用口罩唔衛生，唔想佢哋因為咁嘅原因慳住用，希望可以畀啲優惠佢哋食個飯，然後送兩個口罩畀佢哋，又唔使長者要排隊持拎口罩，希望可以幫到佢哋少少。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">何家梗係唔缺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似去佢間藍店食個麵都過百蚊，老人家依家六折食個麵送兩個口罩，去得食六十幾蚊消費力嘅，恨唔恨你兩個口罩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢個政協護旗手加埋藍店老闆，仲邊有黃絲幫襯呀，依家咪半價劈價博啲老人家幫襯充撐場面，何家淑女唔志在錢，係要面出風頭啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e712283568d668054ed467831dc21950263a84","tid":1914813,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"以前食過一次啲湯唔暖唔熱都算<br />\n麵煮到淋哂都夠膽拎比人食"},{"pid":"0894610c4925bd4b63daca9c74a78a7e6b8514eb","tid":1914813,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2e712283568d668054ed467831dc21950263a84","tid":1914813,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"以前食過一次啲湯唔暖唔熱都算<br />\n麵煮到淋哂都夠膽拎比人食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T19:38:27.000Z","msg":"有錢就是任性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過百蚊一碗牛肉麵<br />\n睇過openrice食評有一期佢做hello kitty主題餐，幾廿蚊一杯特飲，只係加多咗隻爛鬼貓公仔就收人咁嘅價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抵唔抵真係見仁見智<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">不過佛山政協藍店！不了！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2861eaff8fa5f0115a218798c381de741eed7e99","tid":1914813,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T20:09:07.000Z","msg":"如果手足中左招記得去幫襯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7786051504f8e842f803cde31b538e8de83f8555","tid":1914813,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"老實講句, 佢家族要奶共, 佢都身不由己<br />\n<br />\n再加上佢係黃, 放過佢啦"},{"pid":"502439c6f730fcefb5ec8d1d90c58476ba12d64e","tid":1914813,"uid":15647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7786051504f8e842f803cde31b538e8de83f8555","tid":1914813,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"老實講句, 佢家族要奶共, 佢都身不由己<br />\n<br />\n再加上佢係黃, 放過佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"白帶好黃？"},{"pid":"c596b5f6e924f9cd2ad31bb239ebd2c40279f08b","tid":1914813,"uid":71194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"1c3bc914cbf7226154e38ce02eda5ed0f2531f80","tid":1914813,"uid":251110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"何超蓮想有光環姐，所謂慈善都係表面嘢"},{"pid":"0da300ca601ef1a9f6203b4d433212ba925cf842","tid":1914813,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"